{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@discardableResult"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ConnectFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" = ConnectFlags(0), "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14FileMonitorRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitorRef","text":"FileMonitorRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO7FileRefV","text":"FileRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO7FileRefV","text":"FileRef"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FileMonitorEvent","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO16FileMonitorEventa","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitorEvent","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"flags"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The signal handler to call"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Run the given callback whenever the ","type":"text"},{"code":"changed","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" signal is emitted","type":"text"}]}],"name":"handler"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"watchMoves"},{"type":"text","text":" on a directory monitor, and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the information is available (and if supported by the backend),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"eventType"},{"type":"text","text":" may be "},{"code":"renamed","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"movedIn"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"movedOut"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In all cases ","type":"text"},{"code":"file","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be a child of the monitored directory.  For"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"renames, ","type":"text"},{"code":"file","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be the old name and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"otherFile"},{"text":" is the new","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"name.  For “moved in” events, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"file"},{"text":" is the name of the file that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"appeared and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"otherFile"},{"text":" is the old name that it was moved from (in","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"another directory).  For “moved out” events, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"file"},{"type":"text","text":" is the name of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the file that used to be in this directory and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"otherFile"},{"type":"text","text":" is the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"name of the file at its new location."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It makes sense to treat ","type":"text"},{"code":"movedIn","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"equivalent to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"created"},{"type":"text","text":" and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"movedOut"},{"text":" as equivalent to","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"deleted"},{"text":", with extra information.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"renamed"},{"type":"text","text":" is equivalent to a delete\/create"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"pair.  This is exactly how the events will be reported in the case"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that the ","type":"text"},{"code":"watchMoves","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is not in use."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If using the deprecated flag ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"sendMoved"},{"text":" flag and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"eventType"},{"type":"text","text":" is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"moved"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"file"},{"text":" will be set to a ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/File"},{"type":"text","text":" containing the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"old path, and ","type":"text"},{"code":"otherFile","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be set to a "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/File","type":"reference"},{"text":" containing the new path.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In all the other cases, "},{"code":"otherFile","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be set to ","type":"text"},{"code":"NULL","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This represents the underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"changed"},{"text":" signal","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Note"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/filemonitorref\/onchanged(flags:handler:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onChanged"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14FileMonitorRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"FileMonitorRef"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO7FileRefV","text":"FileRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FileRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO7FileRefV"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FileMonitorEvent","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO16FileMonitorEventa"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"title":"onChanged(flags:handler:)","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"extendedModule":"GIO","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:3GIO19FileMonitorProtocolPAAE9onChanged5flags7handlerSi10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV_yAA0bC3RefV_AA0bM0VAMSgSo05GFileC5EventatctF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO14FileMonitorRefV"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitorRef\/onChanged(flags:handler:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitorRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitorRef\/FileMonitorProtocol-Implement